
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;问题列表：<br/>
<div class="errorLibrary_right">
  <div class="searchProblem"><input name="" type="text" class="se_input" value="输入想知道的问题..." /><button class="se_btn">搜索</button></div>
  <div class="answerPro">
    <ul>
      <% @feedbacks.each do |feedback| %>
        <li>
          <div class="an_p danHang" onmouseover="javascript:$('<%= feedback.id %>').style.display='block';" ><a><%= feedback.description %></a></div>
          <div class="an_member" id="<%= feedback.id %>" style="display:none">
              <%if feedback.answer.nil? %>
                <%= "等待回答中..." %>
              <%else%>
                <%=feedback.answer %>
              <%end%>
            </div>
        </li>
      <%end unless @feedbacks.nil?%>
    </ul>
  </div>
</div>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;请在以下输入框输入你遇到的问题：
<input type="hidden" value="<%= @id %>" id="id" name="id"/>
<div class="field">
  &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<textarea cols="30" rows="4"  name="description" id="description">
  </textarea>
</div> 
<div class="actions">
  &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<input  type="button"value="提问" onclick="javascript:feedb('<%= @id %>')" />
</div>